            <div class="card">
                <h3>Early Intervention</h3>
                <p>Supporting infants and toddlers with developmental delays and their families through specialized therapy, education, and family support services. Our early intervention team works with children from birth to age three to maximize their developmental potential.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>School-Age Services</h3>
                <p>After-school and summer programs that provide educational support, recreational activities, and social skill development for children and teens with intellectual and developmental disabilities. We work closely with schools to ensure continuity of care.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Adult Day Programs</h3>
                <p>Structured day services that promote independence, community integration, and personal development. Activities include vocational training, life skills instruction, recreation, and community outings tailored to individual interests and goals.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Supported Employment</h3>
                <p>Job coaching, placement services, and ongoing support to help individuals find and maintain competitive employment in the community. We work with local employers to create inclusive workplaces and provide long-term job retention support.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Residential Services</h3>
                <p>A range of housing options from independent living support to 24-hour residential care. Our residential programs focus on helping individuals develop the skills needed to live as independently as possible while ensuring their health and safety.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Respite Care</h3>
                <p>Temporary care services that give family caregivers a break while ensuring their loved ones receive quality care in a safe, supervised environment. Available for a few hours, overnight, or extended periods.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

