        <h2>Specialized Services</h2>
        <div class="card-grid">
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Behavioral Support</h3>
                <p>Positive behavior support planning and intervention services for individuals with challenging behaviors. Our certified behavior analysts work with individuals, families, and care teams to develop effective strategies.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Therapeutic Recreation</h3>
                <p>Recreational therapy programs designed to improve physical, cognitive, emotional, and social functioning. Activities include adaptive sports, arts and crafts, music therapy, and community recreation.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Transportation</h3>
                <p>Safe, reliable transportation services to help individuals access programs, employment, medical appointments, and community activities. Our trained drivers provide additional support as needed.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

